     <body>
     <div xml:lang="lat" type="poem">
   <pb facs="4"/>
   <head>In Politeuphuian Decastichon.</head>
   <lg>
      <l>MYstica qui sophiae, cultae quadrantia vitae,</l>
      <l>Ingenij varios flores, rimaris, et ardes:</l>
      <l>Intemerata legas huius monumenta laboris.</l>
      <l>In quo feruentem mentis sedabis orexim</l>
      <l>Hoc duce Mercurio, caelesti numine plenus,</l>
      <l>Vertice sublimi feries arcana polorum</l>
      <l>Et facile rapidas fauces vitabis Auerni.</l>
      <l>Omnia sunt in hoc: musis aptissima sedes,</l>
      <l>Virtutis morumque Pharos Cynosur a vaganti</l>
      <l>Ingenij, genij, mentis, rationis acumen.</l>
   </lg>
   <closer>
      <signed>R. A.</signed>
   </closer>
</div>
